## ============================================
## APP WEBHOOK SECRETS (Required for Triggers)
## ============================================
## These secrets are used to verify webhook signatures from external services.
## Without them, triggers for Slack, Square, Intercom, and Facebook Leads won't work.
##
## Format: {"piece-url-name": {"webhookSecret": "SECRET"}}
## 
## Where to get secrets:
##   - Slack: Slack App → Basic Information → Signing Secret
##   - Square: Square Developer Dashboard → Application → Webhook Signature Key
##   - Intercom: Intercom Developer Hub → App Settings → Webhooks → Hub Secret
##   - Facebook Leads: Facebook App → App Secret
##
## Single piece example:
## AP_APP_WEBHOOK_SECRETS='{"@activepieces/piece-slack":{"webhookSecret":"YOUR_SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET"}}'
##
## Multiple pieces example:
## AP_APP_WEBHOOK_SECRETS='{"@activepieces/piece-slack":{"webhookSecret":"SLACK_SECRET"},"@activepieces/piece-square":{"webhookSecret":"SQUARE_SECRET"}}'
##
## TODO: Replace YOUR_SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET with your actual Slack signing secret
AP_APP_WEBHOOK_SECRETS='{"@activepieces/piece-slack":{"webhookSecret":"44a41f9cb32e6297acb88817399b3688"}}'
